            <div class="row ">
              <div class="col-lg-12">
                <h3 class="features-medium-heading">Understanding the Solution's Revenue Opportunity</h3>
                <p>TAM helps you create a user focused strategy by setting your concerned market apart from the global market.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-6 features-item from-down slide-in">
            <div class=" f-card">
